  - "B\xE2y gi\u1EDD \u0111ang c\xF3 1 th\xF4ng tin quan tr\u1ECDng trong ph\xF2ng
    kho \u1EDF l\u1EA7u 2, c\u1EADu h\xE3y l\u1EA5y ch\xECa kh\xF3a ph\xF2ng ng\u1EE7
